line.comment: * fn - AddInactiveShips, arg1 - target menu instance
* fn - AddShips, arg1 - target menu instance, arg2 - array of ships
* Build menu options based on array of objects.
* Group options by sectors with optional selectable/non-selectable option for
* In: $SectorAsOption - true/false. If true, then group (sector) will be
* with sector object as return value.
* Add menu info line base on $Base.TextID + 1
* Open menu with title based on $Base.TextID + 2
* Apply color scheme to text representation of object.
* In: $Object.Text - text representation of object (to coloring)
* In: $TextValues - menu entry texts (same order with $DataValues)
* Add inactive ships to menu as options (available for new job)
* In: $Dummy.Args array of (bit mask, text id)
